# Payload CMS Projektstruktur

## Hauptkonfiguration:

- [src/payload.config.ts](mdc:src/payload.config.ts) - Payload CMS Hauptkonfiguration
- [src/collections/](mdc:src/collections/) - Collection-Definitionen (Users.ts, Media.ts)
- [src/payload-types.ts](mdc:src/payload-types.ts) - Generierte TypeScript-Typen

## Frontend:

- [src/app/(frontend)/](<mdc:src/app/(frontend)/>) - Frontend-Routen
- [src/app/(payload)/](<mdc:src/app/(payload)/>) - Payload Admin-Interface

## Datenbank:

- Verwendet PostgreSQL mit Supabase
- Konfiguration in [.env](mdc:.env) mit DATABASE_URI
- Docker-Setup in [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml)

## Wichtige Dateien:

- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js Konfiguration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript Konfiguration
